posts.post_title: FS: a few T206 St. Louisans
posts.post_content:
Posted By: steve yawitz
Nothing to write home about, but I have a few collector-grade T206 Cardinals and Browns available. I thought the Williams would receive a numerical grade despite the funky cut, but it ended up with the dread A instead of the 50 I expected. Oh well. Prices include shipping; PayPal's fine with me. Thanks, Steve.
